divs: Sighting Detailsit was shaped oblong and had a baby green light on the back end and at the time of the sighting i was sitting on my porch relaxing and listening to music on the radio but the music wasent loud at all and when i saw the object it was hovering around about 80 ft. away and it was about 20 ft long and it messed up my radio. ...please do not call or text me...
Summary: it was near the ohio river comeing from kentucky.
